
** Proxy

File: /etc/dnf/dnf.conf 
[main]
gpgcheck=1
installonly_limit=3
clean_requirements_on_remove=True
proxy=http://bluecoat:80
proxy_username=svc_oem
proxy_password=xxxxxx


** Install

emacs
cvs
system-config-users
xorg-x11-fonts*
tigervnc

** SSH

systemctl enable sshd.service

** Upgrade

dnf system-upgrade reboot
dnf system-upgrade clean
dnf clean packages


